Package ohos.media.audio

Class SoundPlayer.SoundPlayerParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.media.audio.SoundPlayer.SoundPlayerParameters
  • Enclosing class:
    SoundPlayer

    public static class SoundPlayer.SoundPlayerParameters
extends Object
    Provides SoundPlayer parameters for a playback task.

    This class provides the playback task priority, looping policy, playback speed, and multi-channel volume (defined by AudioVolumes).

    Since:
    1
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Multimedia#AUDIO
